1
00:01:03,439 --> 00:01:04,920
Once I become emperor,

2
00:01:04,959 --> 00:01:06,840
I'll just focus on enjoying life.

3
00:01:07,560 --> 00:01:09,599
As for all these tedious court affairs,

4
00:01:09,840 --> 00:01:11,400
I'll leave them to you, Imperial Brother-in-Law.

5
00:01:13,439 --> 00:01:15,120
Then I thank Your Majesty in advance.

6
00:01:15,519 --> 00:01:16,319
Your Majesty.

7
00:01:17,120 --> 00:01:17,920
Hahaha!

8
00:01:19,200 --> 00:01:20,920
That really is music to my ears.

9
00:01:21,719 --> 00:01:22,599
By the way, Imperial Brother-in-Law,

10
00:01:23,040 --> 00:01:24,920
there's one more thing I need your help with.

11
00:01:25,719 --> 00:01:26,840
Please speak, Your Majesty.

12
00:01:28,239 --> 00:01:29,519
You have no idea.

13
00:01:29,920 --> 00:01:31,560
In order to become emperor,

14
00:01:31,799 --> 00:01:33,120
I followed Qi Zhi all this way.

15
00:01:33,920 --> 00:01:36,040
Not only did he refuse to name me heir,

16
00:01:36,040 --> 00:01:37,480
he gave me trouble at every turn.

17
00:01:37,799 --> 00:01:40,519
He repeatedly threw me in jail as a scapegoat.

18
00:01:41,439 --> 00:01:42,719
Just thinking about it

19
00:01:43,120 --> 00:01:44,799
makes my blood boil.

20
00:01:46,200 --> 00:01:48,120
I want him to watch with his own eyes,

21
00:01:48,480 --> 00:01:50,239
as I, Liu Heng, become emperor,

22
00:01:51,040 --> 00:01:53,319
and marry the woman Qi Zhi loves most.

23
00:01:55,840 --> 00:01:56,719
Hahaha!

24
00:01:57,040 --> 00:01:58,040
Excellent.

25
00:01:58,480 --> 00:02:00,480
Your Majesty truly is ruthless.

26
00:02:02,000 --> 00:02:02,840
Guards!

27
00:02:03,480 --> 00:02:04,840
Bring Qi Zhi out here.

28
00:02:18,400 --> 00:02:19,199
Come, come, come.

29
00:02:19,479 --> 00:02:22,240
Give Special Envoy Qi the best seat.

30
00:02:22,560 --> 00:02:24,280
Let him see it all,

31
00:02:24,280 --> 00:02:25,159
crystal clear.

32
00:02:25,479 --> 00:02:26,719
Hahaha!

33
00:02:39,360 --> 00:02:41,319
Groom, bow!

34
00:02:41,960 --> 00:02:43,560
Bride and groom, take your places.

35
00:02:44,199 --> 00:02:45,000
Offer incense.

36
00:03:12,439 --> 00:03:13,639
Please.

37
00:03:18,960 --> 00:03:20,199
First bow,

38
00:03:20,560 --> 00:03:22,199
to Heaven and Earth.

39
00:03:26,439 --> 00:03:27,319
Ah.

40
00:03:37,520 --> 00:03:38,719
Second bow,

41
00:03:39,000 --> 00:03:40,639
to your parents.

42
00:03:47,159 --> 00:03:47,960
Wait.

43
00:03:49,919 --> 00:03:50,719
Imperial Brother-in-Law,

44
00:03:51,280 --> 00:03:52,439
I have no father or mother left,

45
00:03:52,639 --> 00:03:54,240
and you are the princess's elder brother.

46
00:03:54,639 --> 00:03:55,759
So how about this bow,

47
00:03:56,120 --> 00:03:57,599
we bow to you instead?

48
00:04:01,000 --> 00:04:01,840
Hehehe.

49
00:04:03,599 --> 00:04:06,120
Then I shall respectfully accept.

50
00:04:20,639 --> 00:04:21,439
Imperial Brother-in-Law,

51
00:04:22,319 --> 00:04:24,399
growing up as Father's adopted son,

52
00:04:24,639 --> 00:04:26,720
my royal brothers all looked down on me.

53
00:04:27,199 --> 00:04:28,959
Let alone show any brotherly affection.

54
00:04:30,079 --> 00:04:31,120
How about this?

55
00:04:31,560 --> 00:04:33,399
Let's share a pot of wine today,

56
00:04:33,720 --> 00:04:34,800
and once we finish it,

57
00:04:35,040 --> 00:04:36,439
we can call each other brothers.

58
00:04:36,839 --> 00:04:37,639
How about it?

59
00:04:39,199 --> 00:04:40,000
Guards.

60
00:04:59,000 --> 00:05:00,399
Bring it to the Imperial Brother-in-Law.

61
00:05:05,800 --> 00:05:06,600
Your Majesty,

62
00:05:07,360 --> 00:05:10,399
we can drink after the ceremony, right?

63
00:05:11,839 --> 00:05:15,639
Seems you don't wish to drink with me.

64
00:05:16,160 --> 00:05:17,639
Very well.

65
00:05:17,839 --> 00:05:19,240
I'll drink first as a show of respect.

66
00:05:32,399 --> 00:05:34,360
Your Majesty is so sincere,

67
00:05:36,839 --> 00:05:39,079
how could I not return the gesture?

68
00:05:48,560 --> 00:05:51,240
From now on, we are brothers.

69
00:05:52,199 --> 00:05:53,800
And from now on, we shall together...

70
00:05:54,680 --> 00:05:55,639
Heh.

71
00:05:59,000 --> 00:05:59,800
Brothers?

72
00:06:00,839 --> 00:06:02,519
Who's your brother, Ouyang Que?

73
00:06:06,959 --> 00:06:07,759
My surname is Liu.

74
00:06:13,160 --> 00:06:14,519
What on earth are you trying to do?

75
00:06:15,759 --> 00:06:17,120
You become emperor,

76
00:06:17,720 --> 00:06:18,519
and we...

77
00:06:19,000 --> 00:06:21,240
each get what we want. Isn't that fine?

78
00:06:22,199 --> 00:06:23,759
I owe Father a great debt of gratitude.

79
00:06:24,800 --> 00:06:27,120
How could I hand Daliang to an outsider?

80
00:06:29,240 --> 00:06:30,959
If you die here with me,

81
00:06:31,839 --> 00:06:34,079
won't the throne just go to your brothers?

82
00:06:34,839 --> 00:06:35,800
Heh.

83
00:06:36,839 --> 00:06:38,519
We brothers can fight over it.

84
00:06:40,519 --> 00:06:42,279
But for an outsider like you to try?

85
00:06:42,639 --> 00:06:43,639
No way.

86
00:06:44,000 --> 00:06:45,120
Let me tell you.

87
00:06:50,240 --> 00:06:51,079
Liu Heng!

88
00:06:52,680 --> 00:06:54,199
Hahaha!

89
00:06:59,439 --> 00:07:00,240
Liu Heng!

90
00:07:00,560 --> 00:07:01,360
Liu Heng!

91
00:07:03,759 --> 00:07:05,360
Liu Heng!

92
00:07:08,839 --> 00:07:09,680
Brother!

93
00:07:20,399 --> 00:07:23,839
As Grand Secretary of Liang, I swear to you,

94
00:07:24,240 --> 00:07:25,079
the Daliang Kingdom

95
00:07:25,759 --> 00:07:27,920
will surely send troops to aid Yan Kingdom.

96
00:07:28,759 --> 00:07:30,519
As long as you put down your blades,

97
00:07:31,519 --> 00:07:32,839
I will spare your lives.

98
00:07:35,240 --> 00:07:36,959
Don't listen to his nonsense!

99
00:07:37,720 --> 00:07:39,000
Kill him!

100
00:07:40,680 --> 00:07:42,000
Hah!

101
00:07:46,800 --> 00:07:48,120
The Second Under Heaven is here!

102
00:07:50,240 --> 00:07:51,360
Who else wants a piece of me?

103
00:07:52,839 --> 00:07:54,120
I'll say it once more.

104
00:07:55,839 --> 00:07:56,639
Daliang

105
00:07:57,759 --> 00:07:59,639
will surely help the Yan Kingdom.

106
00:08:00,560 --> 00:08:01,560
Put down your blades.

107
00:08:04,000 --> 00:08:04,800
Drop them!

108
00:08:08,040 --> 00:08:09,920
Liu Heng.

109
00:08:17,480 --> 00:08:19,040
I've already crippled his martial arts.

110
00:08:20,240 --> 00:08:21,079
The rest

111
00:08:21,279 --> 00:08:22,079
is up to you.

112
00:08:22,079 --> 00:08:22,879
Mm.

113
00:08:23,480 --> 00:08:24,279
Guards!

114
00:08:24,920 --> 00:08:26,639
Throw Ouyang Que in prison!

115
00:08:29,319 --> 00:08:30,839
Prince Huai!

116
00:08:32,279 --> 00:08:33,080
Prince Huai!

117
00:08:33,240 --> 00:08:34,440
Twenty-Eighth Brother!

118
00:08:46,080 --> 00:08:48,039
You're awake, you're awake.

119
00:08:52,840 --> 00:08:53,639
Bookworm.

120
00:08:55,519 --> 00:08:56,360
I'm sorry.

121
00:08:57,600 --> 00:09:00,240
For causing you so much trouble along the way.

122
00:09:00,919 --> 00:09:01,519
Sigh.

123
00:09:02,679 --> 00:09:04,480
But you should actually thank me.

124
00:09:06,159 --> 00:09:07,320
If it weren't for me,

125
00:09:07,799 --> 00:09:09,799
making things hard for you and Ouyang Yan,

126
00:09:10,679 --> 00:09:12,200
you two wouldn't be together.

127
00:09:12,480 --> 00:09:13,480
Am I right?

128
00:09:14,399 --> 00:09:15,240
Don't say that.

129
00:09:15,679 --> 00:09:16,759
Don't talk like that.

130
00:09:16,960 --> 00:09:17,840
You have to live.

131
00:09:18,240 --> 00:09:20,039
You must live to fight for the throne, right?

132
00:09:20,320 --> 00:09:22,080
You must live to become emperor, right?

133
00:09:22,240 --> 00:09:22,679
Ah.

134
00:09:22,679 --> 00:09:24,840
Haha.

135
00:09:24,960 --> 00:09:27,320
I'm tired.

136
00:09:28,080 --> 00:09:29,159
I can't fight for it anymore.

137
00:09:31,879 --> 00:09:33,200
But at least,

138
00:09:33,799 --> 00:09:35,039
before I die,

139
00:09:36,240 --> 00:09:38,159
I finally got to be emperor once.

140
00:09:38,840 --> 00:09:39,879
Heh.

141
00:09:44,120 --> 00:09:45,679
Liu Heng.

142
00:09:45,960 --> 00:09:46,639
Twenty-Eighth Brother.

143
00:09:46,759 --> 00:09:47,120
Liu Heng.

144
00:09:47,120 --> 00:09:47,919
Twenty-Eighth Brother.

145
00:09:49,360 --> 00:09:50,159
Heh heh.

146
00:09:51,200 --> 00:09:54,240
Never thought I'd be brought down by Liu Heng.

147
00:09:54,240 --> 00:09:55,360
Hahaha.

148
00:09:55,600 --> 00:09:56,399
Ouyang Que.

149
00:09:57,519 --> 00:09:58,960
Even without the Twenty-Eighth Brother,

150
00:09:59,639 --> 00:10:01,840
other brothers would have stepped up one after another.

151
00:10:03,320 --> 00:10:05,120
You underestimated the Daliang Kingdom.

152
00:10:05,639 --> 00:10:06,840
I accept my fate.

153
00:10:08,039 --> 00:10:10,039
Kill me or torture me, do as you wish.

154
00:10:10,159 --> 00:10:10,960
Heh.

155
00:10:11,519 --> 00:10:12,120
Hahaha.

156
00:10:12,600 --> 00:10:14,240
You treat human life like dirt.

157
00:10:14,440 --> 00:10:15,759
The Crown Prince is nothing like you.

158
00:10:17,679 --> 00:10:18,480
Right.

159
00:10:19,600 --> 00:10:20,960
He is nothing like me.

160
00:10:21,200 --> 00:10:23,200
He's a useless fool who only knows how to paint.

161
00:10:25,240 --> 00:10:27,600
If he actually had what it takes to kill me,

162
00:10:28,039 --> 00:10:28,679
Heh.

163
00:10:29,159 --> 00:10:30,879
how could his father have died?

164
00:10:31,120 --> 00:10:32,240
What do you mean by that?

165
00:10:33,120 --> 00:10:35,879
Eunuch Gao thought he was lucky to meet the Five Poisons,

166
00:10:36,240 --> 00:10:38,240
and could thus brew that peerless poison.

167
00:10:39,879 --> 00:10:43,840
In truth, I arranged for Eunuch Gao to meet him.

168
00:10:44,879 --> 00:10:46,000
So it was you.

169
00:10:48,720 --> 00:10:50,320
You're nothing but a useless fool.

170
00:10:51,360 --> 00:10:53,000
You were just born lucky.

171
00:10:53,320 --> 00:10:54,919
What makes you better than me?

172
00:10:57,639 --> 00:10:59,039
If you really had the ability,

173
00:10:59,120 --> 00:11:00,559
so what if I killed your father, the Emperor?

174
00:11:00,559 --> 00:11:01,480
Guards!

175
00:11:01,919 --> 00:11:02,759
Hahaha.

176
00:11:02,759 --> 00:11:03,679
Tomorrow at noon,

177
00:11:04,039 --> 00:11:04,960
Ouyang Que will face

178
00:11:05,399 --> 00:11:06,320
death by a thousand cuts.

179
00:11:06,639 --> 00:11:07,960
Crown Prince, please spare his life.

180
00:11:10,159 --> 00:11:10,960
Crown Prince.

181
00:11:11,360 --> 00:11:12,159
Ouyang Que's

182
00:11:12,240 --> 00:11:13,120
crimes are unforgivable.

183
00:11:13,480 --> 00:11:14,080
But

184
00:11:14,679 --> 00:11:17,000
he's the only family I have left.

185
00:11:20,440 --> 00:11:23,039
Crown Prince, please spare his life.

186
00:11:24,039 --> 00:11:24,679
Crown Prince,

187
00:11:24,919 --> 00:11:26,600
Dubian Kingdom is currently attacking Yan.

188
00:11:26,600 --> 00:11:27,840
If Yan is defeated,

189
00:11:27,840 --> 00:11:29,639
our Daliang would be next to fall.

190
00:11:29,960 --> 00:11:30,559
Why not

191
00:11:31,080 --> 00:11:32,240
send Ouyang Que back,

192
00:11:32,240 --> 00:11:33,679
and let him atone for his crimes?

193
00:11:33,720 --> 00:11:34,519
Qi Zhi.

194
00:11:35,000 --> 00:11:36,919
Don't think I don't know what you're up to.

195
00:11:38,879 --> 00:11:40,360
You want to release Ouyang Que.

196
00:11:40,919 --> 00:11:42,600
You don't have any selfish motives at all?

197
00:11:49,360 --> 00:11:51,240
The Crown Prince is just provoked by Ouyang Que.

198
00:11:51,360 --> 00:11:52,600
The Crown Prince isn't that kind of person.

199
00:11:52,600 --> 00:11:53,600
He's soft-hearted.

200
00:11:53,600 --> 00:11:54,519
He will let him go.

201
00:11:54,679 --> 00:11:55,120
Get up.

202
00:11:55,240 --> 00:11:56,360
Don't help them up.

203
00:11:57,480 --> 00:11:58,240
These few

204
00:11:58,480 --> 00:11:59,600
are all birds of a feather.

205
00:12:01,919 --> 00:12:03,480
Qi Zhi visited so many cities,

206
00:12:04,399 --> 00:12:06,320
yet brought back not a single prince.

207
00:12:08,039 --> 00:12:08,639
Hmph.

208
00:12:09,840 --> 00:12:12,000
So he plotted it all with those two siblings.

209
00:12:13,360 --> 00:12:14,159
Crown Prince,

210
00:12:15,120 --> 00:12:17,519
I admit I was selfish about Ouyang Yan,

211
00:12:17,559 --> 00:12:19,799
but to Daliang, I've never been disloyal.

212
00:12:20,240 --> 00:12:20,840
Hmph.

213
00:12:21,600 --> 00:12:22,440
Daliang?

214
00:12:24,120 --> 00:12:26,480
I think you mean Dubian Kingdom.

215
00:12:27,679 --> 00:12:29,240
The Grand Scholar is your uncle.

216
00:12:30,240 --> 00:12:34,000
Don't you want Dubian Kingdom to invade?

217
00:12:34,320 --> 00:12:34,919
Huh?

218
00:12:35,360 --> 00:12:36,480
Prince Qi Zhi.

219
00:12:39,039 --> 00:12:43,000
You doubt me over one anonymous letter?

220
00:12:43,960 --> 00:12:44,759
Oh, no.

221
00:12:45,799 --> 00:12:47,799
You never trusted me at all.

222
00:12:49,600 --> 00:12:51,440
First you threatened me with Huahua,

223
00:12:51,600 --> 00:12:55,200
then you came along to watch my every move.

224
00:12:55,480 --> 00:12:57,240
Finally, you used Uncle Liu to test me.

225
00:12:57,240 --> 00:12:58,639
You're the one who's been deceiving me.

226
00:12:59,360 --> 00:13:01,360
And you got others to deceive me too.

227
00:13:01,799 --> 00:13:03,039
Crown Prince, don't get worked up.

228
00:13:03,360 --> 00:13:04,879
Qi Zhi has been our friend for so long.

229
00:13:04,879 --> 00:13:05,879
How could he deceive you?

230
00:13:05,879 --> 00:13:06,679
Shut up.

231
00:13:08,039 --> 00:13:09,440
You're pleading for them?

232
00:13:10,240 --> 00:13:12,200
Do you want to betray me alongside them?

233
00:13:18,159 --> 00:13:18,759
Hmph.

234
00:13:19,879 --> 00:13:21,399
I used to think

235
00:13:22,240 --> 00:13:24,759
novels are written because drama mirrors life.

236
00:13:26,039 --> 00:13:27,200
Now I see

237
00:13:27,440 --> 00:13:29,039
life mirrors drama, Crown Prince.

238
00:13:38,159 --> 00:13:38,759
Hmph.

239
00:13:40,039 --> 00:13:41,320
I get it now.

240
00:13:42,720 --> 00:13:44,320
All this time I thought

241
00:13:44,320 --> 00:13:46,039
you saw us as friends.

242
00:13:46,320 --> 00:13:47,559
But now I see,

243
00:13:48,399 --> 00:13:50,279
in your eyes, there are no friends,

244
00:13:50,879 --> 00:13:52,320
only ruler and subjects.

245
00:13:52,639 --> 00:13:53,240
Your Highness,

246
00:13:54,039 --> 00:13:55,480
please eat at least a little.

247
00:13:56,120 --> 00:13:57,440
If you ruin your health,

248
00:13:57,840 --> 00:13:59,039
that would be terrible.

249
00:14:01,440 --> 00:14:02,720
Consort Zhen has arrived.

250
00:14:08,639 --> 00:14:09,679
You're leaving?

251
00:14:10,200 --> 00:14:11,000
Mm.

252
00:14:14,759 --> 00:14:15,639
Makes sense.

253
00:14:17,399 --> 00:14:18,320
I'm sorry.

254
00:14:19,399 --> 00:14:20,519
For bringing you back to the palace,

255
00:14:21,679 --> 00:14:23,159
making you go through so much

256
00:14:23,559 --> 00:14:24,799
that you never should have.

257
00:14:26,200 --> 00:14:27,159
Crown Prince,

258
00:14:27,240 --> 00:14:28,480
let's leave together.

259
00:14:45,039 --> 00:14:46,200
This palace

260
00:14:48,039 --> 00:14:49,440
is like a cage.

261
00:14:51,720 --> 00:14:53,639
I'm fated to remain here.

262
00:14:57,159 --> 00:14:58,600
But you're different.

263
00:15:00,240 --> 00:15:01,679
You still have other choices.

264
00:15:05,559 --> 00:15:06,559
These past days,

265
00:15:06,759 --> 00:15:08,240
you seem like a different person.

266
00:15:12,919 --> 00:15:14,759
I've just grown lonelier,

267
00:15:16,639 --> 00:15:18,399
just like every emperor.

268
00:15:19,240 --> 00:15:19,960
Consort Zhen,

269
00:15:19,960 --> 00:15:21,240
your carriage is here.

270
00:15:23,440 --> 00:15:24,240
Crown Prince,

271
00:15:33,480 --> 00:15:34,679
take care on the road.

272
00:15:35,519 --> 00:15:36,320
Ah.

273
00:15:47,960 --> 00:15:49,320
I still prefer

274
00:15:49,600 --> 00:15:51,039
the Crown Prince who drew comics.

275
00:15:52,039 --> 00:15:53,879
Heh.

276
00:16:07,600 --> 00:16:07,960
Mm.

277
00:16:07,960 --> 00:16:09,799
Don't you regret it at all?

278
00:16:13,039 --> 00:16:15,039
I just hate that my plan wasn't thorough,

279
00:16:15,960 --> 00:16:17,200
falling short at the last moment.

280
00:16:17,559 --> 00:16:18,159
Hmph.

281
00:16:19,960 --> 00:16:20,840
What about me?

282
00:16:23,120 --> 00:16:23,960
Father?

283
00:16:24,080 --> 00:16:25,000
Mother?

284
00:16:27,320 --> 00:16:28,960
You don't care at all?

285
00:16:33,039 --> 00:16:35,039
In a few hours, I'll be dead.

286
00:16:36,440 --> 00:16:38,919
Right now I only care about this bowl of rice.

287
00:16:39,960 --> 00:16:42,240
I need a full belly before I go.

288
00:16:45,159 --> 00:16:45,960
Brother,

289
00:16:50,039 --> 00:16:51,159
hurry and go.

290
00:16:55,120 --> 00:16:56,559
Don't come at noon, alright?

291
00:17:07,599 --> 00:17:09,160
I only regret one thing.

292
00:17:14,200 --> 00:17:15,680
I regret

293
00:17:17,519 --> 00:17:19,160
that I couldn't claim this throne

294
00:17:19,559 --> 00:17:20,839
before your wedding.

295
00:17:24,200 --> 00:17:26,680
I regret not letting you marry the one you love.

296
00:17:30,640 --> 00:17:31,759
I regret

297
00:17:32,039 --> 00:17:33,839
making you marry for Yan Kingdom's sake.

298
00:17:40,880 --> 00:17:41,680
Brother.

299
00:18:22,039 --> 00:18:22,839
Qi Zhi.

300
00:18:24,799 --> 00:18:26,200
Are you going to kill me?

301
00:18:34,960 --> 00:18:35,960
Just a bit of sedative.

302
00:18:36,319 --> 00:18:37,599
When I come back,

303
00:18:37,960 --> 00:18:38,920
do whatever you want with me.

304
00:18:48,279 --> 00:18:49,799
Hurry, go!

305
00:18:49,799 --> 00:18:51,720
Or the Crown Prince will arrest you too.

306
00:18:54,440 --> 00:18:55,480
By order of the Crown Prince:

307
00:18:55,839 --> 00:18:57,559
Ouyang Que is spared from death.

308
00:18:57,759 --> 00:18:59,279
Special Envoy Qi Zhi is dispatched

309
00:18:59,559 --> 00:19:01,799
to escort Ouyang Que back to the Yan Kingdom.

310
00:19:04,119 --> 00:19:04,920
Special Envoy Qi,

311
00:19:06,559 --> 00:19:07,799
why haven't you released him yet?

312
00:19:08,720 --> 00:19:09,519
Special Envoy,

313
00:19:09,839 --> 00:19:11,119
without an imperial decree,

314
00:19:11,559 --> 00:19:12,799
please don't put me in a tough spot.

315
00:19:12,799 --> 00:19:13,599
Will this do?

316
00:19:31,519 --> 00:19:33,359
Guards!

317
00:19:33,839 --> 00:19:35,079
Guards!

318
00:19:59,799 --> 00:20:00,599
Teacher.

319
00:20:02,119 --> 00:20:02,920
Save me.

320
00:20:03,559 --> 00:20:05,119
Someone drugged me.

321
00:20:06,279 --> 00:20:07,599
Save me.

322
00:20:10,279 --> 00:20:12,039
I'm sorry, Your Highness.

323
00:20:13,440 --> 00:20:15,480
The emperor of Daliang Kingdom

324
00:20:15,960 --> 00:20:18,200
must be Qi Zhi.

325
00:20:21,599 --> 00:20:22,599
You...

326
00:20:23,920 --> 00:20:25,759
You really are in this together.

327
00:20:52,880 --> 00:20:54,079
This is as far as I can take you.

328
00:20:54,240 --> 00:20:54,839
Remember,

329
00:20:55,000 --> 00:20:56,119
I didn't save you out of personal favor,

330
00:20:56,119 --> 00:20:57,039
but for your Yan Kingdom.

331
00:20:57,039 --> 00:20:57,880
You're going back?

332
00:20:58,240 --> 00:20:58,839
Yes.

333
00:20:59,119 --> 00:20:59,839
No.

334
00:20:59,960 --> 00:21:01,119
The Crown Prince will kill you.

335
00:21:01,640 --> 00:21:02,960
I'm a subject of Daliang.

336
00:21:03,039 --> 00:21:04,119
I can't leave.

337
00:21:06,640 --> 00:21:07,720
I understand.

338
00:21:07,880 --> 00:21:08,480
But...

339
00:21:10,319 --> 00:21:11,640
If I make it back,

340
00:21:11,640 --> 00:21:13,319
meet me at Qingshui Lake in three days.

341
00:21:13,319 --> 00:21:14,559
If I don't return,

342
00:21:15,720 --> 00:21:16,599
forget me.

343
00:21:24,480 --> 00:21:25,279
If you don't come,

344
00:21:26,319 --> 00:21:27,920
I'll wait for you forever.

345
00:21:56,640 --> 00:21:57,480
Your Highness.

346
00:22:00,079 --> 00:22:01,119
Sigh.

347
00:22:08,039 --> 00:22:09,559
They're long gone.

348
00:22:11,160 --> 00:22:13,039
There's no need to be too distraught.

349
00:22:14,480 --> 00:22:17,279
I remember when the Prince first came to make me his special envoy,

350
00:22:17,279 --> 00:22:18,799
it was you who came to persuade me.

351
00:22:20,519 --> 00:22:24,680
I didn't think I'd fail even his last wish.

352
00:22:25,039 --> 00:22:25,880
No.

353
00:22:28,119 --> 00:22:29,319
You found him.

354
00:22:30,440 --> 00:22:31,640
You found him.

355
00:22:32,160 --> 00:22:32,880
In his heart,

356
00:22:34,200 --> 00:22:35,720
the most perfect successor

357
00:22:42,039 --> 00:22:43,279
is you yourself.

358
00:23:01,519 --> 00:23:02,640
Little sister,

359
00:23:04,440 --> 00:23:05,759
our great vengeance

360
00:23:08,160 --> 00:23:09,759
is about to be fulfilled.

361
00:23:25,160 --> 00:23:25,960
Qi Zhi.

362
00:23:27,559 --> 00:23:28,960
The fact that you came here

363
00:23:29,759 --> 00:23:31,640
means you've made up your mind.

364
00:23:32,279 --> 00:23:33,839
Your mother

365
00:23:34,680 --> 00:23:36,559
was a princess of the Dubian Kingdom.

366
00:23:38,480 --> 00:23:40,160
Your real father

367
00:23:40,599 --> 00:23:42,559
was the late Emperor of Daliang.

368
00:23:43,599 --> 00:23:44,519
And I

369
00:23:46,759 --> 00:23:48,400
am your real uncle.

370
00:23:50,720 --> 00:23:52,319
Teacher, what are you saying?

371
00:23:55,880 --> 00:23:57,759
When your mother married into Daliang,

372
00:23:58,960 --> 00:24:00,400
we always

373
00:24:00,599 --> 00:24:02,119
kept in touch through letters.

374
00:24:02,720 --> 00:24:04,720
She truly did live

375
00:24:05,599 --> 00:24:07,839
a very happy life for a time.

376
00:24:08,480 --> 00:24:09,279
But

377
00:24:10,240 --> 00:24:11,519
as relations between the Dubian Kingdom

378
00:24:11,519 --> 00:24:13,599
and Daliang gradually broke down,

379
00:24:14,599 --> 00:24:16,000
your mother

380
00:24:16,279 --> 00:24:18,000
was driven out of the palace

381
00:24:18,000 --> 00:24:19,319
by the Empress of Daliang.

382
00:24:22,400 --> 00:24:23,519
Not long after,

383
00:24:26,599 --> 00:24:28,000
she passed away.

384
00:24:30,319 --> 00:24:32,240
I was the one who brought you back

385
00:24:34,039 --> 00:24:35,559
and placed you in a private school.

386
00:24:36,079 --> 00:24:36,680
And then,

387
00:24:38,079 --> 00:24:38,680
I

388
00:24:39,480 --> 00:24:41,279
changed my name and came to Daliang.

389
00:24:42,400 --> 00:24:43,599
Until today.

390
00:24:47,720 --> 00:24:48,640
Right now, in all of Daliang,

391
00:24:51,039 --> 00:24:53,400
you are the only heir left.

392
00:24:56,279 --> 00:24:58,039
I had originally decided

393
00:24:58,559 --> 00:24:59,880
that I would

394
00:25:00,160 --> 00:25:01,640
ascend the throne and become Emperor.

395
00:25:03,200 --> 00:25:04,119
But

396
00:25:12,000 --> 00:25:14,000
that day, I had a fight with the Crown Prince.

397
00:25:14,759 --> 00:25:16,920
I said he didn't treat me as a friend.

398
00:25:18,240 --> 00:25:19,960
But I was wrong.

399
00:25:20,480 --> 00:25:21,279
Qi Zhi.

400
00:25:22,599 --> 00:25:24,160
The Crown Prince is already gone.

401
00:25:24,599 --> 00:25:26,400
What you should care about now

402
00:25:26,400 --> 00:25:28,599
is the people of the entire realm.

403
00:25:29,599 --> 00:25:30,200
No.

404
00:25:30,519 --> 00:25:32,640
The Crown Prince could have escaped that day.

405
00:25:32,640 --> 00:25:33,640
It was because of me.

406
00:25:33,880 --> 00:25:34,480
Qi Zhi,

407
00:25:34,960 --> 00:25:36,440
you can't blame yourself.

408
00:25:36,880 --> 00:25:38,480
The Crown Prince had been drugged that day.

409
00:25:38,480 --> 00:25:40,039
That's why he couldn't escape.

410
00:25:40,160 --> 00:25:40,960
No.

411
00:25:46,039 --> 00:25:47,839
How do you know he was drugged?

412
00:25:49,920 --> 00:25:50,960
Silly child.

413
00:25:52,240 --> 00:25:53,440
The coroner

414
00:25:53,440 --> 00:25:56,440
examined all the food in the Prince's room that day.

415
00:25:57,039 --> 00:25:58,640
Of course I know.

416
00:26:01,799 --> 00:26:03,759
But I'm the one who killed the Crown Prince.

417
00:26:04,759 --> 00:26:06,640
I was the one who drugged him.

418
00:26:07,960 --> 00:26:09,160
I can't take the throne.

419
00:26:09,880 --> 00:26:11,200
I can't be this Emperor.

420
00:26:12,240 --> 00:26:13,720
I can't be this Emperor.

421
00:26:14,480 --> 00:26:15,480
I can't.

422
00:26:22,519 --> 00:26:23,359
That's right.

423
00:26:24,799 --> 00:26:26,279
For this very reason,

424
00:26:28,960 --> 00:26:30,200
indulging in trifles ruins one's resolve.

425
00:26:31,160 --> 00:26:32,480
Could it be

426
00:26:32,839 --> 00:26:34,960
that you want to end up like the Crown Prince?

427
00:26:36,759 --> 00:26:37,880
No, no, you can't.

428
00:26:44,200 --> 00:26:45,759
You're the one who killed the Crown Prince.

429
00:26:46,519 --> 00:26:47,799
You murdered him.

430
00:26:50,839 --> 00:26:52,759
Hmph.

431
00:26:53,640 --> 00:26:55,839
You're even sharper than your mother.

432
00:26:56,599 --> 00:26:59,400
Her mind-reading couldn't read kin's hearts,

433
00:27:00,160 --> 00:27:01,359
but yours can.

434
00:27:02,640 --> 00:27:04,519
But the Crown Prince respected and loved you.

435
00:27:04,559 --> 00:27:05,839
He called you his teacher.

436
00:27:05,880 --> 00:27:06,880
Why did you kill him?

437
00:27:06,880 --> 00:27:07,640
Right.

438
00:27:08,559 --> 00:27:10,480
If not to put you on the throne,

439
00:27:10,720 --> 00:27:12,480
why would I bother killing the Crown Prince?

440
00:27:14,039 --> 00:27:17,200
All my years of hardship were for this day of yours.

441
00:27:17,319 --> 00:27:18,640
Yet you,

442
00:27:19,720 --> 00:27:23,359
are so cowardly and utterly disappointing.

443
00:27:25,119 --> 00:27:27,039
But the Crown Prince was innocent!

444
00:27:27,160 --> 00:27:27,960
Innocent?

445
00:27:30,359 --> 00:27:31,799
Then let me ask you this.

446
00:27:32,519 --> 00:27:33,799
Years ago,

447
00:27:34,400 --> 00:27:36,000
your mother,

448
00:27:36,319 --> 00:27:39,799
branded a witch for her mind-reading and cast out,

449
00:27:39,799 --> 00:27:41,119
died on the road.

450
00:27:41,559 --> 00:27:42,400
Was she

451
00:27:42,519 --> 00:27:43,640
innocent or not?

452
00:27:44,799 --> 00:27:45,599
And what about

453
00:27:46,880 --> 00:27:48,279
the Emperor of Daliang,

454
00:27:49,359 --> 00:27:51,160
who seized our nation's lands,

455
00:27:51,400 --> 00:27:52,640
and the countless souls

456
00:27:52,640 --> 00:27:54,400
who perished at his hands?

457
00:27:54,759 --> 00:27:55,480
Were they

458
00:27:56,160 --> 00:27:57,400
innocent or not?

459
00:28:00,960 --> 00:28:03,319
I've endured humiliation all these years

460
00:28:03,839 --> 00:28:05,359
just to witness with my own eyes

461
00:28:05,960 --> 00:28:07,240
the downfall of Daliang.

462
00:28:10,440 --> 00:28:12,559
How are you any different from Ouyang Que?

463
00:28:12,599 --> 00:28:13,400
I am.

464
00:28:15,799 --> 00:28:17,599
The difference between us is this:

465
00:28:19,119 --> 00:28:21,160
I will see, with my own eyes,

466
00:28:21,720 --> 00:28:23,279
all of my ambitions

467
00:28:24,960 --> 00:28:26,640
come to fruition.

468
00:28:28,480 --> 00:28:29,640
You want me to take the throne?

469
00:28:30,319 --> 00:28:31,640
You want me to be Emperor?

470
00:28:32,559 --> 00:28:33,640
Just kill me instead.

471
00:28:33,640 --> 00:28:34,440
Fine.

472
00:28:35,039 --> 00:28:36,519
Then I'll grant your wish.

473
00:28:37,200 --> 00:28:38,279
But

474
00:28:38,640 --> 00:28:39,880
before that,

475
00:28:40,319 --> 00:28:43,319
I'll kill that witch Ouyang Yan first

476
00:28:43,799 --> 00:28:45,160
to bury alongside you.

477
00:28:45,279 --> 00:28:46,559
Don't try to scare me.

478
00:28:46,559 --> 00:28:47,400
Scare you?

479
00:28:48,480 --> 00:28:49,359
Hmph.

480
00:28:50,759 --> 00:28:53,119
Hahahaha.

481
00:28:54,920 --> 00:28:56,480
At this very moment, Ouyang Yan

482
00:28:56,480 --> 00:28:57,799
is at Qingshui Lake.

483
00:28:58,480 --> 00:29:00,319
She's surrounded by my men.

484
00:29:00,960 --> 00:29:01,960
If you don't believe me,

485
00:29:03,119 --> 00:29:04,319
go ahead and try.

486
00:29:10,359 --> 00:29:11,160
No!

487
00:29:11,160 --> 00:29:12,200
Don't hurt her.

488
00:29:13,599 --> 00:29:15,119
I beg you, don't hurt her.

489
00:29:16,160 --> 00:29:17,279
Don't hurt her.

490
00:29:18,240 --> 00:29:19,359
Please don't hurt her.

491
00:29:21,599 --> 00:29:22,480
I'm begging you.

492
00:29:22,480 --> 00:29:23,279
I'll take the throne.

493
00:29:23,759 --> 00:29:24,920
I'll ascend right now.

494
00:29:28,079 --> 00:29:29,039
If

495
00:29:30,319 --> 00:29:32,119
you don't rule properly as Emperor,

496
00:29:33,599 --> 00:29:35,839
then prepare to claim her corpse.

497
00:29:37,599 --> 00:29:39,559
I mean every word.

498
00:30:03,640 --> 00:30:04,960
The late Emperor passed suddenly,

499
00:30:05,240 --> 00:30:06,319
returning to the five elements.

500
00:30:06,799 --> 00:30:08,839
I receive the mandate of Heaven,

501
00:30:08,960 --> 00:30:10,359
and the grand blessings of the sages.

502
00:30:10,920 --> 00:30:13,160
By the late Emperor's final decree,

503
00:30:13,440 --> 00:30:18,880
I now proclaim to Heaven and Earth my ascension to the throne.

504
00:30:22,480 --> 00:30:24,440
You enthroned a new emperor on your own?

505
00:30:24,640 --> 00:30:25,960
Is there no law left in this land?

506
00:30:26,000 --> 00:30:28,400
Even if the new Emperor is the late Emperor's flesh and blood,

507
00:30:28,480 --> 00:30:29,720
mere words are no proof.

508
00:30:30,359 --> 00:30:31,160
Gentlemen.

509
00:30:32,119 --> 00:30:33,160
I know.

510
00:30:33,160 --> 00:30:34,640
You four ministers are of great virtue and renown,

511
00:30:34,880 --> 00:30:37,519
appointed by the late Emperor to assist the Crown Prince.

512
00:30:38,200 --> 00:30:40,119
But the Crown Prince is now dead,

513
00:30:40,359 --> 00:30:42,319
and the new Emperor ascends tomorrow.

514
00:30:42,920 --> 00:30:44,200
So,

515
00:30:44,200 --> 00:30:45,799
since you ministers are advanced in years,

516
00:30:46,039 --> 00:30:47,400
there's no need

517
00:30:48,119 --> 00:30:49,480
to trouble yourselves any further.

518
00:30:49,759 --> 00:30:50,559
You...

519
00:30:51,039 --> 00:30:51,880
This...

520
00:30:53,279 --> 00:30:54,279
What is the meaning of this?

521
00:30:55,240 --> 00:30:57,480
Are you telling us to retire to our hometowns?

522
00:30:57,920 --> 00:30:58,720
Exactly.

523
00:30:59,039 --> 00:31:00,279
Gentlemen,

524
00:31:00,279 --> 00:31:02,200
the dynasty's name is about to change.

525
00:31:02,440 --> 00:31:03,279
All of you

526
00:31:03,279 --> 00:31:05,160
are now ministers of the former dynasty.

527
00:31:05,400 --> 00:31:06,880
That you keep your lives at all

528
00:31:07,480 --> 00:31:10,119
is already a great mercy from the new Emperor.

529
00:31:10,559 --> 00:31:12,039
I think you've gone mad!

530
00:31:12,119 --> 00:31:13,799
You clearly intend to commit treason!

531
00:31:14,400 --> 00:31:15,839
Yes, you're plotting rebellion!

532
00:31:16,279 --> 00:31:17,279
Since all of you

533
00:31:17,279 --> 00:31:20,000
are so loyal to the late Emperor,

534
00:31:20,599 --> 00:31:21,200
then

535
00:31:21,599 --> 00:31:23,279
I shall grant your wish.

536
00:31:23,559 --> 00:31:24,160
Guards!

537
00:31:27,799 --> 00:31:29,279
Send them

538
00:31:29,880 --> 00:31:31,000
to join the late Emperor.

539
00:31:31,240 --> 00:31:32,039
Yes, sir!

540
00:31:32,039 --> 00:31:32,839
Traitor!

541
00:31:32,839 --> 00:31:33,640
You traitor!

542
00:31:46,759 --> 00:31:48,200
Guards!

543
00:31:48,200 --> 00:31:49,640
Take these two bronze beasts

544
00:31:49,839 --> 00:31:51,119
and place them beside the dragon throne.

545
00:32:04,880 --> 00:32:06,359
Very well, you may leave.

546
00:32:06,480 --> 00:32:07,279
Yes.

547
00:32:15,640 --> 00:32:16,200
Hey.

548
00:32:16,559 --> 00:32:17,680
You, step aside.

549
00:32:18,880 --> 00:32:19,640
Hey.

550
00:32:20,559 --> 00:32:21,839
Crown Prince, you're alive!

551
00:32:22,920 --> 00:32:24,240
Of course I'm alive.

552
00:32:25,440 --> 00:32:27,319
Otherwise, how could I capture you two traitors?

553
00:32:27,400 --> 00:32:28,519
That's wonderful!

554
00:32:28,519 --> 00:32:29,960
I thought you were dead.

555
00:32:32,000 --> 00:32:32,799
Qi Zhi.

556
00:32:33,240 --> 00:32:34,799
Stop your hypocrisy.

557
00:32:35,119 --> 00:32:37,319
You're sitting here wearing the dragon robe.

558
00:32:37,839 --> 00:32:39,200
What more is there to deny?

559
00:32:40,039 --> 00:32:41,400
And you.

560
00:32:41,400 --> 00:32:42,480
My teacher.

561
00:32:43,400 --> 00:32:45,039
When you set fire to burn me,

562
00:32:45,640 --> 00:32:47,240
you never expected me to return alive, did you?

563
00:32:47,920 --> 00:32:48,920
Your Highness.

564
00:32:49,039 --> 00:32:50,480
What do you mean by that?

565
00:32:50,599 --> 00:32:51,480
Look around.

566
00:32:51,480 --> 00:32:53,359
The proclamations have all been posted.

567
00:32:53,359 --> 00:32:55,039
The coronation is about to begin.

568
00:32:55,039 --> 00:32:56,119
Even if you return,

569
00:32:56,640 --> 00:32:58,359
can you really turn the tide?

570
00:32:59,319 --> 00:33:01,039
I'm going to try anyway.

571
00:33:01,720 --> 00:33:02,279
Guards!

572
00:33:02,640 --> 00:33:04,279
Arrest these two traitors at once!

573
00:33:04,480 --> 00:33:05,279
Guards!

574
00:33:05,559 --> 00:33:06,519
He's the real traitor!

575
00:33:06,519 --> 00:33:07,400
Arrest him!

576
00:33:07,400 --> 00:33:08,759
Who dares touch me? I'm the Crown Prince!

577
00:33:08,759 --> 00:33:09,799
Arrest him!

578
00:33:12,640 --> 00:33:13,440
Qi Zhi.

579
00:33:14,839 --> 00:33:16,559
I treated you like a brother,

580
00:33:17,839 --> 00:33:19,559
yet now you want to seize the throne.

581
00:33:20,640 --> 00:33:22,400
I never thought of such a thing.

582
00:33:23,200 --> 00:33:24,279
At this point,

583
00:33:24,880 --> 00:33:27,039
I have no desire to explain further.

584
00:33:28,799 --> 00:33:30,839
I won't believe anything you say anymore.

585
00:33:32,359 --> 00:33:33,599
You two,

586
00:33:34,440 --> 00:33:35,640
one drugged me,

587
00:33:36,759 --> 00:33:38,000
the other set the fire.

588
00:33:39,000 --> 00:33:40,000
The two of you,

589
00:33:41,039 --> 00:33:43,039
you wanted me dead all along, didn't you?

590
00:33:43,400 --> 00:33:44,880
Calm down, Crown Prince.

591
00:33:45,200 --> 00:33:46,319
Let's talk this out.

592
00:33:46,319 --> 00:33:48,799
If killing me will ease your hatred,

593
00:33:49,720 --> 00:33:50,920
then go ahead and kill me.

594
00:33:51,359 --> 00:33:51,960
You...

595
00:33:52,759 --> 00:33:53,559
Fine.

596
00:33:54,640 --> 00:33:55,759
I'll grant your wish today.

597
00:33:55,839 --> 00:33:56,759
No!

598
00:34:01,640 --> 00:34:02,319
Uncle!

599
00:34:04,279 --> 00:34:04,920
Uncle!

600
00:34:06,279 --> 00:34:06,920
Uncle!

601
00:34:10,639 --> 00:34:11,639
Don't worry about me.

602
00:34:12,480 --> 00:34:13,719
Kill the Crown Prince.

603
00:34:14,639 --> 00:34:15,920
The coronation is what matters.

604
00:34:16,639 --> 00:34:17,480
Hurry!

605
00:34:19,480 --> 00:34:20,159
Uncle!

606
00:34:20,519 --> 00:34:21,199
Uncle!

607
00:34:23,239 --> 00:34:24,400
Kill him.

608
00:34:29,320 --> 00:34:31,440
It's the only way left now.

609
00:34:38,280 --> 00:34:39,280
Argh!

610
00:34:43,400 --> 00:34:45,760
In the end, you never saw me as a brother.

611
00:34:48,960 --> 00:34:49,760
Hmph.

612
00:34:53,000 --> 00:34:55,280
Did you ever see me as one either?

613
00:34:58,159 --> 00:34:58,840
Argh!

614
00:35:12,360 --> 00:35:13,159
Argh!

615
00:35:54,480 --> 00:35:55,920
We could go to a small town.

616
00:35:55,920 --> 00:35:57,199
You run a dojo, I run a private school.

617
00:35:57,400 --> 00:35:58,639
We'd teach students together.

618
00:36:00,880 --> 00:36:03,559
Could you go a little easier on me?

619
00:36:05,039 --> 00:36:06,079
I don't want to do this either!

620
00:36:06,280 --> 00:36:08,239
What do you have to be angry at me about?

621
00:36:09,719 --> 00:36:11,199
What's your relationship with Yunxi?

622
00:36:11,320 --> 00:36:13,280
You scoundrel!

623
00:36:13,440 --> 00:36:14,480
Scoundrel!

624
00:36:15,719 --> 00:36:17,440
Ask me, ask me!

625
00:36:20,119 --> 00:36:21,239
Am I pretty?

626
00:36:21,760 --> 00:36:22,760
She's the type

627
00:36:23,280 --> 00:36:27,360
weak stomach, no cold food or scallions.

628
00:36:28,840 --> 00:36:30,599
I have to look after her.

629
00:36:31,920 --> 00:36:32,719
Argh!

630
00:36:32,960 --> 00:36:34,559
With others, I need to sneak a peek,

631
00:36:34,760 --> 00:36:36,000
but with you, I don't.

632
00:36:37,280 --> 00:36:39,400
You need to find an heir to the throne.

633
00:36:39,519 --> 00:36:41,280
I want to be the Empress.

634
00:36:42,519 --> 00:36:43,320
Qi Zhi.

635
00:36:44,760 --> 00:36:45,599
I'm here.

636
00:36:47,239 --> 00:36:48,360
I wanted to say,

637
00:36:48,719 --> 00:36:49,400
a ring,

638
00:36:49,639 --> 00:36:51,000
can always get lost.

639
00:36:51,559 --> 00:36:52,360
But

640
00:36:52,559 --> 00:36:54,079
carved on the body, it can never be lost.

641
00:36:55,000 --> 00:36:56,719
Now that I've carved the ring on my body,

642
00:36:56,760 --> 00:36:58,239
I just want to tell you,

643
00:37:00,239 --> 00:37:01,719
you can never lose me now.

644
00:37:30,360 --> 00:37:31,320
Sir, let me pour you some water.

645
00:37:49,960 --> 00:37:50,639
Boss.

646
00:37:50,760 --> 00:37:52,719
I'll take this book.

647
00:37:53,400 --> 00:37:54,639
I'll take this one too.

648
00:38:18,800 --> 00:38:19,480
Boss!

649
00:38:19,639 --> 00:38:20,440
At your service.

650
00:38:20,760 --> 00:38:22,719
This chicken tastes terrible!

651
00:38:23,119 --> 00:38:24,840
How do you run this business?

652
00:38:25,119 --> 00:38:26,719
I'll smash this place up, I swear!

653
00:38:27,519 --> 00:38:27,960
Oh dear!

654
00:38:28,320 --> 00:38:29,119
I wouldn't dare, I wouldn't dare.

655
00:38:29,119 --> 00:38:30,880
Please enlighten me, miss, please!

656
00:38:32,400 --> 00:38:33,079
Come.

657
00:38:34,159 --> 00:38:35,440
Let me teach you.

658
00:38:36,920 --> 00:38:38,199
Four liang of chicken.

659
00:38:39,280 --> 00:38:40,280
Wash it and add salt.

660
00:38:40,920 --> 00:38:43,480
A little sugar, a little ginger.

661
00:38:43,760 --> 00:38:47,280
Some soy sauce, two qian of star anise.

662
00:38:47,559 --> 00:38:49,039
Two qian of goji berries.

663
00:38:49,760 --> 00:38:51,639
Three liang of yellow wine.

664
00:38:52,320 --> 00:38:53,239
And then,

665
00:39:48,400 --> 00:39:49,079
Oh my!

666
00:39:52,960 --> 00:39:53,760
Your Majesty.

667
00:39:54,480 --> 00:39:55,159
Sit upright like a bell.

668
00:39:57,360 --> 00:39:58,679
I know, I know.

669
00:39:58,679 --> 00:39:59,360
Like a bell.

670
00:40:06,039 --> 00:40:07,599
Your Majesty,

671
00:40:07,960 --> 00:40:09,199
what's wrong with you?

672
00:40:09,599 --> 00:40:10,280
How about

673
00:40:10,559 --> 00:40:12,800
we summon the imperial physician again?

674
00:40:13,679 --> 00:40:14,039
That won't be necessary.

675
00:40:14,400 --> 00:40:15,079
Let's hold court.

676
00:40:23,480 --> 00:40:24,119
Your Majesty.

677
00:40:24,320 --> 00:40:26,599
Mind your appearance.

678
00:40:26,920 --> 00:40:28,440
Aren't you all so annoying?

679
00:40:28,599 --> 00:40:29,280
Hey.

680
00:40:30,280 --> 00:40:30,880
You don't understand.

681
00:40:31,039 --> 00:40:32,480
You don't get it, I have Dragon Robe Phobia!

682
00:40:34,880 --> 00:40:35,559
We know.

683
00:40:36,199 --> 00:40:39,280
But you are the Emperor, after all.

684
00:40:39,559 --> 00:40:42,679
I miss battling Qi Zhi and the others.

685
00:40:43,159 --> 00:40:43,960
Forget it, forget it.

686
00:40:43,960 --> 00:40:44,639
Let's hold court.

687
00:40:45,519 --> 00:40:47,119
Since all you lords are here today,

688
00:40:47,480 --> 00:40:48,840
I have an announcement to make.

689
00:40:49,320 --> 00:40:50,239
I'm abdicating.

690
00:40:50,639 --> 00:40:51,440
Uh, what?

691
00:40:52,039 --> 00:40:52,679
Abdicating again?

692
00:40:52,960 --> 00:40:54,159
What on earth is going on?

693
00:40:55,119 --> 00:40:56,880
Just hurry up and bring Qi Zhi back to me.

694
00:40:57,480 --> 00:40:58,559
Find him and bring him to me at once.

695
00:40:58,559 --> 00:40:59,239
Your Majesty.

696
00:40:59,280 --> 00:41:00,760
Qi Zhi is already dead.

697
00:41:01,079 --> 00:41:02,159
Dead, my foot!

698
00:41:03,480 --> 00:41:05,599
Prince Huai told me about the Tortoise-Breath Powder trick.

699
00:41:06,480 --> 00:41:08,159
Just bring Qi Zhi back to me.

700
00:41:08,159 --> 00:41:08,840
I'm appointing him

701
00:41:09,000 --> 00:41:11,440
as Royal Secret Envoy to Find the Heir,

702
00:41:12,159 --> 00:41:13,320
to bring back the other lost princes

703
00:41:13,719 --> 00:41:14,400
to inherit the throne.

704
00:41:15,039 --> 00:41:15,559
This Emperor thing,

705
00:41:16,000 --> 00:41:16,679
I

706
00:41:16,679 --> 00:41:17,239
will

707
00:41:17,320 --> 00:41:17,880
not

708
00:41:17,880 --> 00:41:18,480
do it!

709
00:41:19,280 --> 00:41:19,960
Your Majesty!

710
00:41:20,360 --> 00:41:21,880
Why is that?

711
00:41:22,000 --> 00:41:24,079
Could you at least give us a reason?

712
00:41:26,039 --> 00:41:26,840
Hmph.

713
00:41:28,039 --> 00:41:29,920
I have 100 reasons not to be Emperor.

714
00:41:31,039 --> 00:41:32,559
But I can't be bothered to explain.

715
00:41:32,800 --> 00:41:33,599
Ugh, court dismissed!
